{"tid":1492530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《記者問》警員協會搞唔搞個集會 撐兩警","createTime":"2019-08-21T01:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T01:18:08.000Z","uid":229835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac230a1c58b2f734dde92a0dac49425e116ffe0a","tid":1492530,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:09:26.000Z","msg":"當年撐警大會 <br />\n<br />\n警察員佐級協會主席陳祖光發言稱現時警員執勤，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不時遭到無理言語、行為挑釁，警員要啞忍是不合理，忍無可忍作出一些行動，卻被指違規甚至違法</span></span></span>。 <br />\n｛今次長者襲警，比言語挑釁更甚，作出一些行動卻被指違法｝<br />\n<br />\n主持感謝特首參選人<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉淑儀、港區全國人大代表譚惠珠、民建聯主席李慧琼、自由黨主席鍾國斌、民建聯葛珮帆、經民聯梁美芬、何君堯、新民黨田北辰、容海恩</span></strong></span></span>出席。<br />\n專欄作家屈穎妍亦獲安排坐在嘉賓席<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有出席過既 都可以問下</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當年七警私下用刑 最終八方支援<br />\n安家費近2000萬 <br />\n今次軍裝同樣私下用刑 會得到支援嗎？<br />\n<br />\n純粹好奇"},{"pid":"f3cee89ef11616dc1412cf412c806b48bd2e6710","tid":1492530,"uid":229835,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"員佐級協會表示<br />\n<br />\n都唔關政治檢控 即割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐，核彈都照撐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db98012cac589761e8b4e5369d5a637fca341cf3","tid":1492530,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"當年七警有 2000萬安家費"},{"pid":"40347eb2ae9ba762d1cdde92a3cc79e099221d15","tid":1492530,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:15:07.000Z","msg":"警方當7位同事係英雄架"},{"pid":"0067dde6aa312037030c1019f7295c3ef3eaafe5","tid":1492530,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:15:26.000Z","msg":"做警察 冇得輸"},{"pid":"769853e2